-- Barclays Hires Vanessa Koo From Goldman Sachs for Chinese Mergers Position
-- Philip Lagerkranser
-- 2010-07-07T02:21:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-07/barclays-hires-vanessa-koo-from-goldman-sachs-for-chinese-mergers-position.html

          
          
             Barclays Plc said it hired Vanessa
Koo from Goldman Sachs Group Inc. as a managing director for
mergers and acquisitions, focusing on China.  
 The U.K. bank also hired James Lim from BNP Paribas SA as
head of real estate coverage for Asia-Pacific, according to an
e-mailed statement.  
          
          


  


        